<title>LATVIA: LATVIA-C.BANK TO SET 7-DAY, 91-DAY REPO AUCTIONS.</title>
<headline>LATVIA-C.BANK TO SET 7-DAY, 91-DAY REPO AUCTIONS.</headline>
<dateline>RIGA 1997-07-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>The central bank said on Friday that from August 1 it would introduce two new repurchase rates: seven-day and 91-day.</p>
<p>The bank said that previously it used 28-day repos.</p>
<p>&quot;The extension to 91 days is aimed at developing the longer-term use of funds obtained by the banks and for longer-term credits for companies and to further the development of Latvia's economy,&quot; the bank said in a statement.</p>
<p>-- Riga newsroom, +371 721 5240</p>
